PROGRAM:
echo "Enter the radius:"
read r
area=`echo 3.14 \* $r \* $r| bc`
cir=`echo 2 \* 3.14 \* $r| bc `
echo "Area : $area"
echo "Circumference : $cir"

OUTPUT:
mlm@mlm-ThinkCentre-E73:~/Desktop/ACN$ chmod +x circle.sh
mlm@mlm-ThinkCentre-E73:~/Desktop/ACN$ ./circle.sh
Enter the radius:
5
Area : 78.50
Circumference : 31.40
